                     <interp inst="t18320517-56-verdict332" type="verdictSubcategory" value="withRecommendation"></interp>
               GUILTY
            </rs>. Aged 44.</p>
               <p>Recommended to Mercy by the Jury - <rs id="t18320517-56-punish333" type="punishmentDescription">
